TOKEN=bot token
CTXWIN=size of history before memorization occurs
SLICEWIN=size of memory summaries, in number of turns
PLACEHOLDER=ID of bot account
TENOR_API_KEY=tenor api key
HF_TOKEN=huggingface token
CHANNELS=channels to listen from, delimited by "|", optional, if needs to be locked down
TRIGGERS=trigger words, delimited by "|"
TRIGTIME=amount of time each trigger lasts, in miliseconds
PYTHON_BIN=preferably an absolute path, path to the virtualenv binary, optional, if run under a virtualenv
MODELPATH=preferably an absolute path, path to the model's .bin
LLMCONFIG=preferably an absolute path, path to the generation config file, e.g. see llm_config.toml
PROMPTFILE=preferably an absolute path, path to the prompt file, e.g. see promptfile